race.description: Superior Oysters Showcase Super Maiden Plate
race.comment: BELLEISTIC BONNY (10) having her third race start after she savaged the line to finish third over 1400m at this track. Blinkers go on and gets in light with the claim. Ticks plenty of boxes. C'MON WICKSY (1) closed strongly when he returned from a break with a solid third over 1175m at Albury. Proven second-up and placed at the trip. Senior rider hops aboard and poses a genuine threat. BRUNDEE TOM (5) will find this more to his liking after resuming with a fading fourth over 1200m at Gosford. Placed second-up in the past and no shock to see him finish over the top of these. REVEILLON (7) came out quickly and had nothing left in the straight with a fading seventh over 1200m at Moruya. Earlier runs had merit and the blinkers come off. Slim place claims. SPLENDID MAGNUS (11) improving filly who stretches out to this trip for the first time fourth-up. Will go back from the draw and surge late.
